## n8n@1.65.0 View the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@1.64.1...n8n@1.65.0) for this version.
**Release date:** 2024-10-24 /// warning | [Breaking change](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/blob/master/packages/cli/BREAKING-CHANGES.md) What changed? Queue polling via the environment variable `QUEUE_RECOVERY_INTERVAL` has been removed. When is action necessary? If you have set `QUEUE_RECOVERY_INTERVAL`, you can remove it as it no longer has any effect. /// This release contains a new features, new nodes, node enhancements, and bug fixes.
